  "imageCount": 6,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/eeb3c522a4664f76.jpg?v=1782539102\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Last weekend I was in Hawaii teaching workshops with Sakura Lala, and we were putting all the finishing touches and details on the <a href=\"https://bookwhen.com/sakuralala\">Tokyo workshops</a> next month. Here are some snapshots of the fun!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/908a0f20cce1d42c.jpg?v=1782539105\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6c-Jack+loves+washi.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f397c2be0e9e7cbc.jpg?v=1782539108\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"6e-All+smiles.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/4dbb82326b91d570.jpg?v=1782539111\">\n</img>\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c92e21632e534388.jpg?v=1782539115\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/839cdf84b6c50fda.jpg?v=1782539118\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Mahalo as always for the amazing Hawaii ladies who joined us!</p><p>So excited about teaching for the first time in Japan. This won't be my first time in Tokyo, but it will be my first time teaching in Asia, which will mean that I have taught creative classes on every single continent except Antarctica. No plans to ever visit there, and I think it's far too cold to get our craft on there anyway. The save the dates have been up for quite a while, but sign ups just started. Would love to see you or have you spread the word about the two days of fun we have planned. The workshops are the same each day, we just wanted to give everyone a chance to make it. You can find more information <a href=\"https://bookwhen.com/sakuralala\">here</a>.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
